Ugh, this area is particularly awful.\n<Adventurer>

It's nothing but black slimes to the right and
left.\n<Adventurer>

That just means we're getting closer to the
center.\n<Adventurer>

There it is. A landmark. The last party turned
back here.\n<Adventurer>
If there's a target, it's beyond here.\n<Adventurer>
Let's go with all our might.\n<Adventurer>
Oh.\n<Adventurer>
...\n<Adventurer>
...\n<Adventurer>
Uh...oh...\n<Adventurer>
Huge... What in the world is that...\n<Adventurer>
Hey, over there. Look.\n<Adventurer>
Ugh...\n<Adventurer>

Finally, a face-to-face encounter... Heh, just as
the rumors said, a beauty that strikes fear...\n<Adventurer>
The pitiable princess, Serena de Gratia...\n<Adventurer>

$gameScreen.showPicture(30,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-01-表情-目05",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
...\n<Serena>
$gameScreen.showPicture(30,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-01-表情-目02",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
Ugh...\n<Serena>

Even a great noble's princess has ended up like
this... Who knows how many years she's been down
here, birthing failures...\n<Adventurer>

Just to confirm, we don't need to capture her
alive, right?\n<Adventurer>
Yeah. The request is for 'extermination.'\n<Adventurer>
$gameScreen.showPicture(13,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-02-素体-ストレート",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
$gameScreen.showPicture(18,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-02-装飾-ピアス",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
$gameScreen.showPicture(23,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-02-装飾-入れ墨",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
$gameScreen.showPicture(27,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-02-表情-眉05",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
$gameScreen.showPicture(30,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-02-表情-目01",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)

It used to be a rescue mission. But it seems the
client has finally given up...\n<Adventurer>
--Hey, I just made eye contact with her.\n<Adventurer>

It's just a reflex. She's not actually seeing
anything.\n<Adventurer>

...She's strangled many of our colleagues to death
before. Don't even think about trying to save her.\n<Adventurer>
$gameScreen.showPicture(30,"PC001-黒スラ敗北/PC001-黒スラ敗北-02-表情-目02",0,0,80,100,100,255,0)
I know. Just checking.\n<Adventurer>
Alright. I'm ready. Anytime is good.\n<Adventurer>

She's still watching us. The first move is ours
for the taking.\n<Adventurer>

We'll go with plan three. If we do it right, we
can take her head off from the start.\n<Adventurer>
Let's put an end to the poor princess's hell soon.\n<Adventurer>

Yeah. We'll get a hefty sum from Gratia after
all!!\n<Adventurer>
Scene_Recollection.prototype.rngd_exit_scene();
